trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 데이터를 제공는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding"> </xref> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding> event is raised by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartAdding%2A> method just before adding a control to a Web Parts zone.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding>이벤트에 의해 발생 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartAdding%2A>메서드 바로 앞에 웹 파트 영역의 컨트롤을 추가 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartAdding%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding>

trans-unit.source: This event provides an opportunity to cancel the process before it is complete.
trans-unit.target: 이 이벤트는 완료 되기 전에 프로세스를 취소 하는 기회를 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded> event is called after a control has been added to a Web Parts zone.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>이벤트는 컨트롤에 웹 파트 영역에 추가한 후에 호출 됩니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartAddingEventArgs class contains information that can be used within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding> event.
trans-unit.target: WebPartAddingEventArgs 클래스 내에서 사용할 수 있는 정보가 포함 되어는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding>이벤트.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdding>

trans-unit.source: It provides access to the Web Parts control that is being added and the zone it is being added to.
trans-unit.target: 추가 되는 웹 파트 컨트롤 및에 추가 되는 영역에 대 한 액세스를 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartAddingEventArgs"></xref> class.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> (or server or user control) to be added to a Web page or opened on a page.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> (또는 서버 또는 사용자 정의 컨트롤)를 웹 페이지에 추가 하거나 페이지에서 열.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> that `webPart` is being added to.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> 하 `webPart` 에 추가 되 고 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: An integer that represents the ordinal position that `webPart` occupies in `zone`, relative to other controls in `zone`.
trans-unit.target: 서 수를 나타내는 정수 위치를 지정 하는 `webPart` 의 차지 `zone`, 다른 컨트롤에서 상대 `zone`합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Web Parts zone that the Web Parts control is being added to.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 컨트롤에 추가 되는 웹 파트 영역을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> that the Web Parts control is being added to.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> 웹 파트 컨트롤에 추가 되 고 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the index position of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control within its zone.
trans-unit.target: 인덱스 위치를 가져오거나 설정 합니다.는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> 영역 내에서 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The ZoneIndex property indicates the numerical order (or ordinal position) within the zone for the Web Parts control being added in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded> event.
trans-unit.target: ZoneIndex 속성에 추가 되는 웹 파트 컨트롤에 대 한 영역 내에서 순서 (또는 서 수 위치)을 나타냅니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>이벤트.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses this property to track and manage its collection of Web Parts controls on a Web page.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>컨트롤에서이 속성을 사용 하 여 추적 하 고 웹 페이지에 웹 파트 컨트롤의 컬렉션을 관리 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > The value of the ZoneIndex property for a control might not equal the index value for the same control within the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > 컨트롤에 대 한 ZoneIndex 속성의 값 내에서 동일한 컨트롤에 대 한 인덱스 값과 다를 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A>컬렉션.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: The numerical order of a control within its zone.
The first control in a zone has an index value of zero.
trans-unit.target: 영역에 첫 번째 컨트롤에는 인덱스 값이&0;에 있습니다.
